{"task":"transcribe","language":"english","duration":231.58999633789062,"text":"What if you could wake up every morning to new leads in your inbox, qualified prospects who already know, like and trust you, ready to book a discovery call and what if you didn't have to spend hours creating content, writing emails or chasing people in the DMs to make it happen? I'm about to show you how AI can do the heavy lifting so you can focus on what you actually love, coaching. Here's the truth about being a coach in 2026. You're incredible at transforming lives, your clients get results. But when it comes to actually getting those clients? It feels like a second full-time job, you're told to post every day, write emails every week, be everywhere on social media, follow up with leads, nurture your list. And somewhere in all that marketing noise, you're supposed to actually coach. Most coaches burn out. Not because they're bad at coaching, but because they're drowning in marketing tasks that never seem to end. There's got to be a better way. And now, there is. Introducing the AI Client Attraction Suite. This is a complete system that puts AI to work, attracting, nurturing and converting coaching clients for you. We're talking about weeks of content created in minutes, lead magnets that practically write themselves, email sequences that warm up cold leads and book discovery calls on autopilot. This isn't theory. This isn't here's some prompts, good luck. This is a done-for-you system with templates, frameworks and step-by-step implementation you can deploy this week. Here's what you get. Module 1. The AI Content Engine. Generate weeks of high-converting content in minutes. LinkedIn posts, Instagram captions, emails. All done. Module 2. The Lead Magnet Generator. Create irresistible free offers that build your list fast. Guides, checklists, assessments. AI handles it. Module 3. The Automated Nurture System. A seven-email sequence that warms up leads and books calls while you sleep. Module 4. AI Sales Conversations. DM scripts and discovery call frameworks that convert without being pushy. Module 5. The Client Attraction Dashboard. Track your leads, plan your content and follow a 90-day roadmap to consistent clients. Plus three bonuses. 50 proven content hooks, a discovery call script with AI prep and 30 days of private community access. Now, what's this worth? If this system books you just one extra client per month at $2,000, $3,000, $5,000 or more, it pays for itself immediately. Coaches are charging $5,000, $10,000, even $20,000 for similar programs. And they should. Because this works. But I'm not charging $20,000. I'm not even charging $5,000. Your investment today is just $9.97. One time. Full access. Forever. And if you need flexibility, there's a payment plan. Three payments of $3.66. Plus, you're protected by our 30-day first lead guarantee. Implement the system, get your first AI-generated lead within 30 days or get a full refund. No questions asked. Look, you became a coach to change lives. Not to become a full-time marketer. AI is here. It's not going away. The coaches who learn to use it now will build empires. The ones who don't will keep struggling. Which one do you want to be? Click the button below. Get instant access. And let AI start attracting clients for you starting today. I'll see you inside.","words":[{"word":"What","start":0.0,"end":0.2199999988079071},{"word":"if","start":0.2199999988079071,"end":0.36000001430511475},{"word":"you","start":0.36000001430511475,"end":0.41999998688697815},{"word":"could","start":0.41999998688697815,"end":0.6399999856948853},{"word":"wake","start":0.6399999856948853,"end":0.8199999928474426},{"word":"up","start":0.8199999928474426,"end":1.1399999856948853},{"word":"every","start":1.1399999856948853,"end":1.5199999809265137},{"word":"morning","start":1.5199999809265137,"end":1.7000000476837158},{"word":"to","start":1.7000000476837158,"end":1.9800000190734863},{"word":"new","start":1.9800000